data.description: This home qualifies for a grant of $7,500 to $10,000. Ask me how. Welcome to this beautifully renovated 2 bed, 2 bath home, ideally situated for urban convenience minutes away from downtown, Garfield Park, & interstate access. Discover a tastefully renovated interior that seamlessly blends classic Craftsman charm with contemporary design. A bonus room & large enclosed porch can have many potential uses. This home boasts brand-new plumbing, electrical system, & HVAC system, ensuring your peace of mind & long-term comfort. Ample storage space can be found in the dry basement & included garage, offering excess storage. The property's generous double lot provides a spacious backyard perfect for outdoor entertainment. Access to your property is easy with a convenient gravel driveway off the back alley.
